---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="News Hub" 
  lang="en" 
  currentPath="/news/" 
  description="Latest AI News and Breakthroughs"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-400 animate-pulse"></span>
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-300">Live News Feed</span>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
      Neural <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-indigo-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Daily Briefing</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Curated streams of breakthroughs, funding events, and emerging architectures in artificial intelligence.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- News Grid Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <article class="glass-card flex flex-col group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">FUNDING</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">2h ago</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">xAI Raises $6B from Sequoia</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm flex-1 leading-relaxed">Elon Musk's AI venture secures massive funding round at $18B valuation, accelerating Grok development and competing with OpenAI's infrastructure scaling.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/10 text-xs font-medium text-gray-500">Source: TechCrunch</div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <article class="glass-card flex flex-col group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="badge" style="color: #4ade80; background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1); border-color: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.2);">RESEARCH</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">5h ago</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">Meta Unveils Llama 4 Architecture</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm flex-1 leading-relaxed">Rumors confirmed regarding the multi-modal foundations of the upcoming Llama generation, pointing to native real-time video processing capabilities directly embedded in the core weights.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/10 text-xs font-medium text-gray-500">Source: The Verge</div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <article class="glass-card flex flex-col group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="badge" style="color: #f87171; background: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.1); border-color: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.2);">REGULATION</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">1d ago</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors">EU AI Act Enters Implementation Phase</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm flex-1 leading-relaxed">The European Union officially establishes the first comprehensive legal framework for artificial intelligence, classifying systems by risk and imposing strict transparency rules.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/10 text-xs font-medium text-gray-500">Source: Bloomberg</div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <article class="glass-card flex flex-col group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">MODELS</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">1d ago</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">OpenAI Launches GPT-4.5 Ultra</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm flex-1 leading-relaxed">A silent update drops over the weekend, offering 3x faster inference and improved logical reasoning for complex mathematical problems.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/10 text-xs font-medium text-gray-500">Source: Official Blog</div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 5 -->
      <article class="glass-card flex flex-col group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="badge" style="color: #fbbf24; background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); border-color: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2);">HARDWARE</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">2d ago</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">Nvidia B200 Supply Chain Constraints</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm flex-1 leading-relaxed">TSMC reports massive backlog for the next-generation Blackwell chips, extending lead times to 2027 for non-tier-1 hyperscalers seeking infrastructure capabilities.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/10 text-xs font-medium text-gray-500">Source: Reuters</div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 6 -->
      <article class="glass-card flex flex-col group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">STARTUPS</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">3d ago</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Mistral AI Expands Market Share</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm flex-1 leading-relaxed">The European open-weight champion successfully captures 15% of the enterprise API market, challenging the dominance of traditional closed-source providers in the B2B sector.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/10 text-xs font-medium text-gray-500">Source: Sifted</div>
      </article>
      
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* 補充在各分頁內使用的 Tailwind class (因為不想在 Astro config 中裝大包外掛, 所以用標準 CSS) */
  .max-w-7xl { max-width: 80rem; }
  .mx-auto { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .px-6 { padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem; }
  .py-24 { padding-top: 6rem; padding-bottom: 6rem; }
  .pb-24 { padding-bottom: 6rem; }
  .text-center { text-align: center; }
  
  .inline-flex { display: inline-flex; }
  .flex { display: flex; }
  .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }
  .items-center { align-items: center; }
  .justify-between { justify-content: space-between; }
  .gap-2 { gap: 0.5rem; }
  .gap-6 { gap: 1.5rem; }
  .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }
  
  .px-3 { padding-left: 0.75rem; padding-right: 0.75rem; }
  .py-1 { padding-top: 0.25rem; padding-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .mb-3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .mb-4 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .mb-6 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .mt-6 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .pt-4 { padding-top: 1rem; }
  
  .rounded-full { border-radius: 9999px; }
  .w-1\.5 { width: 0.375rem; }
  .h-1\.5 { height: 0.375rem; }
  
  .border { border-width: 1px; }
  .border-t { border-top-width: 1px; }
  .border-white\/10 { border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
  .bg-white\/5 { background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
  .backdrop-blur-sm { backdrop-filter: blur(4px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px); }
  
  .text-xs { font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1rem; }
  .text-sm { font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.25rem; }
  .text-lg { font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.75rem; }
  .text-xl { font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.75rem; }
  .text-5xl { font-size: 3rem; line-height: 1; }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .md\:text-xl { font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.75rem; }
    .md\:text-7xl { font-size: 4.5rem; line-height: 1; }
  }
  
  .font-semibold { font-weight: 600; }
  .font-bold { font-weight: 700; }
  .tracking-widest { letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  .tracking-tight { letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
  .uppercase { text-transform: uppercase; }
  .font-mono { font-family: var(--font-mono); }
  
  .text-gray-300 { color: #d1d5db; }
  .text-gray-400 { color: #9ca3af; }
  .text-gray-500 { color: #6b7280; }
  .text-blue-400 { color: #60a5fa; }
  .text-transparent { color: transparent; }
  
  .max-w-2xl { max-width: 42rem; }
  .leading-relaxed { line-height: 1.625; }
  
  .bg-gradient-to-r { background-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--tw-gradient-stops)); }
  .from-blue-400 { --tw-gradient-from: #60a5fa; --tw-gradient-stops: var(--tw-gradient-from), var(--tw-gradient-to, rgba(96, 165, 250, 0)); }
  .to-indigo-400 { --tw-gradient-to: #818cf8; }
  .bg-clip-text { -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; }
  
  .animate-pulse { animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: .5; } }
  
  .grid { display: grid; }
  .grid-cols-1 { grid-template-columns: repeat(1, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  @media (min-width: 768px) { .md\:grid-cols-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); } }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .lg\:grid-cols-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); } }
  
  .transition-colors { transition-property: color, background-color, border-color, text-decoration-color, fill, stroke; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); transition-duration: 150ms; }
  .group:hover .group-hover\:text-blue-400 { color: #60a5fa; }
  .group:hover .group-hover\:text-green-400 { color: #4ade80; }
  .group:hover .group-hover\:text-red-400 { color: #f87171; }
  .group:hover .group-hover\:text-yellow-400 { color: #fbbf24; }
</style>
